Params: {1: 'Assets/Product/Texture/Image/BgStory/Bgstory92.png'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Staessen', 3: "Everything's just not going to plan...", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Staessen', 3: 'What do you think, 【kuroname】?', 4: '1'}
{2: 'What I think?', 3: '7'}
{2: "Why don't we lay out all the cards on the table?", 3: '8'}
{2: "Don't just stick to your hand.", 3: '9'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Sergey', 3: "...Staessen, where did you find this young 'un?", 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Staessen', 3: 'This is the Gray Raven Commandant. We were finally able to bring closure to Derek and Amberia thanks to this person.', 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Antonov', 3: '...Oh! You\'re "the" commandant?', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Antonov', 3: "Why didn't you say so! Have a seat! Bring me a glass of the best kvass!", 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Sergey', 3: 'First of all, the Commune wants a secure place to live. The two icebreakers are our only hope of survival. However, they also limit our population.', 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Rosetta', 3: 'The Forest Guards are willing to accept absolution and move to a new settlement, provided that the interests of others are not harmed.', 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Antonov', 3: 'Wait... We might have something on our hands here!', 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Staessen', 3: 'This... might work.', 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Sergey', 3: 'So, if the Forest Guards are willing to clear safe passage for a land-based supply route, the Commune can sail the ships to New Murmansk without worries.', 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Rosetta', 3: 'Once we resupply at New Murmansk, the Commune and Forest Guards will set out toward the new settlement.', 4: '1'}

{1: '1', 2: 'Staessen', 3: 'And with a new transportation line established, the ARU can also establish contact with you. The new environment will be far more hospitable than where you live now!', 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Antonov', 3: '...Looks like we were too focused on ourselves.', 4: '1'}
{1: '2', 2: 'Sergey', 3: "If that's the case, we'd be more than willing.", 4: '2'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Rosetta', 3: 'The Forest Guards are also willing to comply with this operation.', 4: '1'}
